      • AuthDescriptor

        public AuthDescriptor(IAuthData authData,
              DefinitionScope scope)
        Serialize an authentication data in a new descriptor.

        Only data given by IAuthData.serialize() are kept when writing this descriptor.

        The given authentication data is retained with all its data and will be returned by getData().

        Parameters:
        authData - the data to serialize.
        scope - definition scope
